                    <span>Hi<BR>I happened to pick up your book, "Lethal Guardian" the other day. You did a fabulous job with the telling of this story. The details and the depth of your book pulled me into the story right away. In fact, I liked it so much I went to the store today and bought your first book, "Perfect Poison." I usually only read Anne Rule's books as far as true crime goes. I was delighted to discover another worthy writer, like yourself, in this genre. <BR>I just wanted to encourage you to continue with your writing. You have been given a gift! Now, go take on the day.... :-)</span>
                  
